Root path
---------

/items

Query params
------------

** id: id of the requested item
** filters: optional additional filters

Result
------

item or null

Example for articles
--------------------

Query: ../api/item/1

{
  "id": 1,
  "type": "article",
  "headline": "Hello world!",
  "description": "Short article description",
  "image": "http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Capture-d’écran-2018-01-19-à-13.12.48.png",
  "body": "Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!",
  "authorName": "user",
  "datePublished": "2018-01-24T13:51:56+0000", // ISO8601
  "dateModified": "2018-01-26T12:59:32+0000",  // ISO8601
  "categories": [
    {
      "name": "Test2",
      "filter": {
        "category": "test2"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Uncategorized",
      "filter": {
        "category": "uncategorized"
      }
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "tag1",
      "filter": {
        "post_tag": "tag1"
      }
    }
  ]
}

